{"tid":715121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬灣居民海中示威抗削渡輪","createTime":"2018-06-24T08:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T11:18:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ab26fb9537c7ef0527e4d9b46cdaa1a70636786","tid":715121,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T08:26:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180624/20429770\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180624%2F20429770&d=bckJ5nBkCG1TFIvHuFK0OsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4da4f893\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180624%2F20429770&h=74416bbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180624/20429770</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月24日 <br />\n<br />\n馬灣居民海中示威抗削渡輪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180624/large/24la3p7new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180624%2Flarge%2F24la3p7new.jpg&h=e06e3c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■示威者游至防鯊網外高舉「反對CUT船」標語。張志華攝 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】經營馬灣水陸兩路交通的珀麗灣客運有限公司，近日計劃削減非繁忙時段馬灣來往中環渡輪班次及提高巴士價格，有馬灣居民昨發起示威活動，由馬灣東灣游出沙灘範圍，在海中心高舉大型標語，反對船公司削減船次及提高巴士價格。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不滿政府無表態<br />\n<br />\n示威者昨早9時由馬灣東灣泳灘出發，其間有救生員及康文署職員到場勸阻，但示威者堅持游至泳灘對出的防鯊網外，高舉「反對CUT船」標語，大喊「反對cut船、反對加價」等口號，亦有近30名居民在泳灘上支持及和應。示威者其後游至珀麗灣碼頭，其間再舉起標語及高呼口號，岸上居民亦有和應口號。<br />\n<br />\n活動發起人倫先生指，「（珀麗灣客運）近10幾年間到𠵱家，船隻或者巴士嘅班次已經不斷削減，𠵱家一邊削減渡輪服務，一邊又削減巴士同埋加價」，令人擔憂馬灣日後的交通服務。<br />\n<br />\n倫先生又批評將馬灣來往中環的渡輪班次削減的舉動「膽大包天」，惟政府對此毫無表態，希望可以透過示威行動讓當局知道馬灣居民的訴求，馬灣的交通問題不能坐視不理。<br />\n<br />\n■記者馮智敏  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n被指膽怯　陳日君：教宗感到我憂慮<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n慶回歸藝術裝置被嘲如圍欄"},{"pid":"274301ce32db4db37215060096e8762a37d733e2","tid":715121,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:30:24.000Z","msg":"自己搞條村船航線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510a7271b34529d853d496c28916cfef5ab156e1","tid":715121,"uid":12021,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:35:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a42d0119a4021c6c253c9e5283bb3bee94f16534","tid":715121,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:36:01.000Z","msg":"佔嶺海域，暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ff4ea809e8af7f455d1a7fc6f562af82dc232b","tid":715121,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"274301ce32db4db37215060096e8762a37d733e2","tid":715121,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:30:24.000Z","msg":"自己搞條村船航線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"之後又會嫌貴。<br />\n有巴士咪算係咁，遲d巴士都cut埋你"},{"pid":"5cc1015c87d16300fd6ff45a3c1c31c70334b3cc","tid":715121,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T11:18:19.000Z","msg":"太激進"}]}